Create $profile
===============
Check if its there:
  Test-Path $PROFILE

If not, make it (defaults to Users\~\Documents\WindowsPowerShell):
  New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path (Split-Path $PROFILE) -Force
  New-Item -ItemType File -Path $PROFILE -Force

Stuff to add:
==============

# Use which like linux
Set-Alias -Name which -Value Get-Command

# salm:triple-chime
# remember, echo ctrl-g is a single chime
function salm{1..3|%{[System.Media.SystemSounds]::Exclamation.Play();Start-Sleep 1}}

# lalm: perpetual chime
function lalm{while($true){[System.Media.SystemSounds]::Exclamation.Play();Start-Sleep 1}}
